# 10. End-to-end result

Now the flow becomes:

1. User logs in through Arthur Core
2. Arthur Core redirects to:

   ```text
   /post-login?code=...
   ```
3. Other app exchanges code with Arthur Core
4. Other app creates Spring Security session
5. Other app redirects to `/home`
6. `/home` sees authenticated user

