# 12. One thing to watch

If your other app is a SPA and not a server-rendered Spring MVC app, the pattern changes a bit:

* frontend reads `code`
* frontend sends code to its backend
* backend calls Arthur Core exchange
* backend creates session

If your other app is Spring MVC or Spring Boot backend first, the code above is the right starting point.

